To run a PlumeMoM & Hysplit simulation

1. Edit input_file.py 

2. Execute run_plumemom_hysplit.sh   - To run the PlumeMoM & Hysplit simulation

3. Execute create_plots.sh           - HYSPLIT plotting routines for solid particles and gas concentrations

4. Execute plot_part_deposit.sh       - To plot the deposit

5. Execute plot_part_air.sh           - To plot atmospheric particle concentration

6. Execute plot_gas_air.sh            - To plot atmospheric concentration of volcanic gasses different than water vapour

7. Execute extract_samples.py        - To extract particles mass loading at specific lat-lon locations (see input_file.py)

8. Execute calculate_part_mass.sh    - To compute the mass of solid particles in the domain 

9. Execute calculate_gas_mass.sh     - To compute the mass of volcanic gases in the domain

10. Execute clean_all.py              - To clean the working directory

From point 3 to point 10 the execution order can be varied by the user
